fields.name: currentMaxLogSize
fields.description: The maximum size the current log is allowed to grow to

fields.name: currentLogSize
fields.description: Approximate amount of space in log currently occupied

fields.name: entryCount
fields.description: Number of entries in the log. Note: for circular logs this value will decrease when a group of entries is deleted to make space for new ones.

fields.name: oldestYear
fields.description: Oldest entry UTC year (1-65635) or zero if there are no entries with known time

fields.name: newestYear
fields.description: Newest year (1-65635) or zero if there are no entries with known time

bits.name: recording
bits.description: Log entry recording is currently turned on

bits.name: inactive
bits.description: Logging system not active - no log present

bits.name: circular
bits.description: The current log is circular
